Theresa May, as Home Secretary and Prime Minister, was warned by police about the effect of the Conservatives' cuts, taking 21,000 police off our streets.</p>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">It is not good enough for <a href="/theresa_may" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="747807250819981312"><s>@</s><b>Theresa_May</b></a> to say NHS problems are "frustrating" and "disappointing" when the Tory Government has caused this crisis. 

Nurses, doctors and patients are pleading with her to properly fund our health service, but she is ignoring them.

The British Government must condemn this dangerous act and work for a just and viable settlement of the conflict.</p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I have spoken with many voters concerned about <a href="/theresa_may" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="747807250819981312"><s>@</s><b>theresa_may</b></a> plans for repealing hunting ban. Labour policy is clear. No to fox hunting.<a href="https://t.co/6pDS2cczgr" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/tom_watson/status/870187413670424577" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/tom_watson/status/870187413670424577"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/tom_watson/sta</span><span class="invisible">tus/870187413670424577</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Shabbir Aslam added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/tom_watson/status/870187413670424577" data-conversation-id="870187413670424577" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="870187413670424577" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="tom_watson" data-user-id="14190551" href="/tom_watson/status/870187413670424577" data-conversation-id="870187413670424577" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
            <div class="QuoteMedia">
      <div class="QuoteMedia-container js-quote-media-container">
